Even though smartphone ’ s apps like Fitbit were able to track our activity earlier, they gave us no reason to exercise like this game does.
The new will lose its appeal and use will diminish over time.
Due to Pokemon ’ s success, however, there will be more games that will combine apps and virtual reality with getting active in the real world, helping many people on the hunt to be more active, fitter and healthier.
